  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueWriter<RuntimeException>
    class CompositeGenericKey
extends GenericKey
    GenericKey which has an array of GenericKey inside and can therefore hold composite key state. For single-keys please instead use the more efficient GenericKey.
